						<div class="postbody">That might be a good idea, except that &lt; &gt; are two additional characters I don't believe are implemented into the romhack as of yet, (thought they could be) and they are also two characters, which is problematic as the Rockman 3/4/5/6 textbox is limited to 24 characters per line, two lines at a time. Adding in two characters every time a new character speaks is expensive in terms of the limited spacing. <br /><br />I like what you've done though. Using your fonts, could you create some example words consisting of the following characters: <br /><br />g j o p q ! ?<br /><br />Perhaps <br /><br />Megaman jumps over powerups quickly!?</div>

